<div id="employer-box">
  <h1>Salon Employers</h1>
  <p>Post job openings, booth rentals, and salon for sale from the fastest growing salon professional network site on the web.</p>
  <p>Every month tens of thousands of salon professionals visit SalonPals to network and looking for new opportunities.
  	 For an afforable monthly fees, you can advertise your open positions, booth rentals, or salon for sale to these
  	 professionals and gain access to profiles of those have registered with us.</p>
  <%= content_tag :button, :type => :submit, :id => :signup do -%>Signup or Create Post<% end -%>
</div>

<div id="profile-box">
  <h1>Salon Professionals</h1>
  <p>Create a FREE profile on the fastest growing salon professional network site on the web.</p>
  <p>Every month thousands of salon employers visit SalonPals to network and recruiting salon professionals for new opportunities.
  	   By registering and creating a profile with SalonPals, you can advertise your skill sets open positions to these employers. You
  	   can also connecting with other fellow salon professionals once registered.</p>
  <%= content_tag :button, :type => :submit, :id => :create_profile do -%>Create Profile<% end -%>
</div>

